{"id":317950,"type":2,"name":"抗戰歌輯","summary":"《抗战歌辑》是万氏兄弟在抗战时期编导的动画，它将流行较广的抗战歌曲和动画结合起来，其中有冼星海作词作曲的《马儿跑》，有刘雪庵根据岳飞原词谱曲的《满江红》，有贺绿汀作词作曲的《保家乡》、《巾帼英雄》、《募寒衣》、《五月纪念歌》，有盛家伦作词作曲的《上前线》，还有武汉合唱团演唱的《长城谣》、《打回老家去》等。万氏兄弟精心绘制的动画，形象地配合了激动人心的歌声，鼓舞了民众的斗志。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>抗战歌辑</li><li><span>话数: </span>7</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/15676\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">万古蟾</a>、<a href=\"/person/15675\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">万籁鸣</a>、<a href=\"/person/22173\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">万超尘</a>、<a href=\"/person/33269\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">万涤寰</a></li><li><span>原画: </span><a href=\"/person/15676\">万古蟾</a>、<a href=\"/person/15675\">万籁鸣</a>、<a href=\"/person/22173\">万超尘</a>、<a href=\"/person/33269\">万涤寰</a></li><li><span>上映年度: </span>1938年</li><li><span>音乐: </span>冼星海、刘雪庵、贺绿汀、盛家伦</li><li><span>制作: </span>中国电影制片厂</li>","collection":{"collect":2},"tags":[{"name":"中国","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":986136,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/986136","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":986137,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/986137","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":986138,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/986138","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":986139,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/986139","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":986140,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/986140","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":986141,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/986141","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":986142,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/986142","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":33269,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b0/